{"tid":581392,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看著他笑","createTime":"2018-03-05T10:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T10:26:26.000Z","uid":66839,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d046f54839301a70ebb22380dd44b348a66a6d98","tid":581392,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T10:05:46.000Z","msg":"有的叫道：「雲加，你積分榜又添上新笑話了！」他不回答，對櫃裡說：「溫兩碗酒，要一條美羊。」便排出五千萬鎊。他們又故意的高聲嚷道：「你一定又害球隊失分了！」雲加睜大眼晴說：「你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你作客升班馬白禮頓，被吊打。」雲加便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道：「黑哨不能算數&hellip;&hellip;算數！&hellip;&hellip;軍醫都智障，能算敗麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「留力歐霸」，什麼「最好的人已在陣中」之類，引得眾人都哄笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"09a85e15d11b89383b40e926d894729d6c4ebb6e","tid":581392,"uid":130790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T10:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401e0915768612bf2a9b129756a047e4eedf7487","tid":581392,"uid":74207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T10:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91558cff63fa974de6883960af29c406b013e19","tid":581392,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T10:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659e4f2a1af3f14916171508e211495fd480798f","tid":581392,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T10:13:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老味係街忍笑忍得好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663774ab629d7f4c934a2317871395bea3f8d788","tid":581392,"uid":63936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T10:13:58.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb18c88382dd94d121e62df8db4482a880b9059","tid":